/v2/users/current.description: Returns the currently logged in user or Unauthorized.

/v2/users/current/applications.description: All of a users applications and only applicable to the currently logged in user.

/v2/users/current/exports/<id>.description: Download Exports from the Recruiter Admin System.

/v2/users/current/orgs.description: Returns a list of recruiters this user has memberships for. This can also be search against by the recrutier name.
